cs.NI, cs.DC, cs.AR, cs.SY, cs.OS 

This paper discusses the use of RDMA in datacenter networks, which is a topic related to network infrastructure (cs.NI) and datacenter architecture (cs.DC). The paper proposes an improved RoCE NIC design, which involves changes to the network architecture (cs.AR) and system design (cs.SY). The paper also discusses the performance implications of these changes, which is related to operating systems (cs.OS).
